P.R. Page, ``8Be nuclear data evaluation'', LANL Memo              419 1451
T-16:NW-18/6-04. Data for MT=600 (with energy range in eV in       419 1451
brackets) come from Koehler 1988 (0.0253-13530) and Cervena 1989   419 1451
(0.0253).                                                          419 1451
                                                                   419 1451
